        "biotoolsCURIE": "biotools:speci",
        "biotoolsID": "speci",
        "description": "Species identification tool using genomic sequences to delineate prokaryotic species. It facilitates fast, accurate and automated taxonomic assignments of newly sequenced genomes based on comparisons of 40 universal, single-copy phylogenetic marker genes extracted from a comprehensive database of sequenced prokaryotic genomes.",
